platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: 我们常常会对着堆积如山的票据和文件发愁，想整理却又无从下手。《Scanner Pro》让你再也不用为此为难。它就像一台便携扫描仪，能将各种纸质文件拍摄下来，自动检测边缘、纠正形状、移除阴影、噪点和杂质，转化成完美的 PDF 文档，方便你分享或打印。此外，《Scanner Pro》还能识别文字、合并文件、识别票据并归档。让你轻松远离那些整理纸张的日子。

Looking to clear out some extra space in the bottom of your closet? You can start with all those boxes of receipts and documents, thanks to Scanner Pro. Convert PDFs into searchable text, merge documents and track receipts. With everything in your pocket, you’ll never need to take time out of the day to hunt down that important form again.

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.sh.k: Quickly scan and save your documents.
